skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: beach sounds
des: Aloha! Let the beautiful sounds of the ocean calm your soul. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Beach Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
